# Product classification

The following fields are used for product classification

- Name
- Ticker
- Remarks
# Free text remark for LLM to consume
- Risk rating
- Expected return
- Currency

# For irrelevant asset classes like Precious Metal, this will be leaving as N/A
- Region
- Country
- Sector

- Asset Classes
  - Equity
  - Bond
  - Precious Metal
  - Balanced
  - Money Market
  - FX
  - Structured Product
    - Principal protected : Y/N
    Name: FCN, CMT RA
  - Annuity
  - Crpyto Currency

- Vehicle
  - ETF
  - Mutual Fund
    - Strategy
    - Theme
    - Domicile
  - Structured Product
  - Insurance

- 

Please refer to docs/spec/risk_rating.md for the detail risk rating.
  
